com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.tracing

Interface JavacPhaseTracer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TranslatingJavacPhaseTracer

    public interface JavacPhaseTracer
    An interface for tracing the phases of compilation in Oracle's javac. This interface is loaded in the system class loader so that it is common to both Buck and compiler plugins.
